  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Displaying SR Flows</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loio8d7acb53f0f67314e10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Displaying SR Flows </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> You can display flows transferred into the SR system (statutory reporting flows) to monitor the position.\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Prerequisites\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Prerequisites</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> You have transferred flows into the statutory reporting ledger.\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Activities\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Activities</h2>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Displaying flows as local actual document display</span>\n</p>\n<ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">In the statutory reporting menu, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Statutory Reporting Flows</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">FI-SL: Local Actual Document Display</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> (transaction <span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">GD23</span>).\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> To limit the selection, make the required mandatory entries.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Execute</span>.\n</p></li></ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Displaying flows as line items</span>\n</p>\n<ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">In the statutory reporting menu, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Flows</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Select FI-SL Line Items</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> (transaction <span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">ISSR_GD20</span>).\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> To limit the selection, make the required mandatory entries.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Execute</span>.\n</p></li></ol>\n</div>\n<div class=\"sectiondiv\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">Displaying flows as totals record</span>\n</p>\n<ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\">In the statutory reporting menu, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Statutory Reporting Flows</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Totals Record Display</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> (transaction <span class=\"ph emphasis emphasis\">ISSR_GD13</span>).\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> To limit the selection, make the required mandatory entries.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Execute</span>.\n</p><aside class=\"note\" aria-labelledby=\"n0t\"><div class=\"title\" id=\"n0t\"><strong>Note</strong></div>\n<p class=\"p\"> The following functions are available in the application:\n</p></aside><div class=\"table-wrapper tablenoborder\"><table summary=\"\" class=\"table\" frame=\"border\" border=\"1\" rules=\"all\"><colgroup><col width=\"50%\"><col width=\"50%\"></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><tr class=\"row\"><th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d843282e185\"><p class=\"p\"> Function\n</p></th><th class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" id=\"d843282e189\"><p class=\"p\"> Explanation\n</p></th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"tbody\"><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d843282e185 \"><p class=\"p\"> Settings\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d843282e189 \"><p class=\"p\"> You can choose between ALV grid and list output; you also have the option to use a user-defined table as a template. This allows you to exclude certain fields from the display.\n</p><p class=\"p\">To access the function, choose <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Extras</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Settings</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> (F2 key) or the relevant pushbutton in the toolbar.\n</p></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d843282e185 \"><p class=\"p\"> User table\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d843282e189 \"><p class=\"p\">By choosing <span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Extras</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Maintain User Table</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span> (key combination SHIFT+F1 or the relevant pushbutton), you can navigate to the identically named Customizing activity.\n</p></td></tr><tr class=\"row\"><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d843282e185 \"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph menucascade\"><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstart.gif\" alt=\"Start of the navigation path\" title=\"Start of the navigation path\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Extras</span>&nbsp;<img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navstep.gif\" alt=\"Next navigation step\" title=\"Next navigation step\">&nbsp;<span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Exit: Authorization....</span><img src=\"themes/sap-light/img/navend.gif\" alt=\"End of the navigation path\" title=\"End of the navigation path\"></span>\n</p></td><td class=\"entry\" style=\"vertical-align:top;\" headers=\"d843282e189 \"><p class=\"p\"> You can restrict the display of certain table fields by defining user profiles.\n</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div></li></ol>\n</div>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
}